This port contains the Smallstep step-ca command line client cli.

It can be used together with the Smallstep certificates step-ca.
step-ca is a local CA. It can be used to create your own local PKI
Infrastructure and includes things like e.g. the possibility to have your
own ACME server.

A zero trust swiss army knife for working with X509, OAuth, JWT, OATH OTP, etc.

WWW: http://www.smallstep.com
GIT: https://github.com/smallstep
